Ingoro y’umurage y’ibidukikije ya Karongi iherere mu ntara y' iburengera zuba bw'u[[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] ,iyi ngoro  bise ingoro y’amababa atatu kubera ibice bitatu biyigize, harimo igice cy’ingufu zisaza, icy’ingufu zisubiramo ndetse n’icy’ibimera, yubatswe ahanini na Leta y’u [[Rwanda]] ariko hiyongera n’igice gito cy’inkuga y’Ubudage n’Ubububiligi yuzuye itwaye amafaranga miliyari na miliyoni miliyoni magana atatu (1,300,000000Rwf)<ref>https://igihe.com/ubukerarugendo/inzu-ndangamurage/article/karongi-babonye-ingoro</ref> <ref>Minisitiri Habineza arasaba ko ingoro y’ibidukikije ya Karongi yafungurwa vuba - Kigali Today</ref>.

== Amateka y'ingoro ndangamurage y'ibidukikije ==
Mu 2015 nibwo ingoro ndangamurage y’ibidukikije ibitse ibikorwa bitandukanye by’urusobe rw’ibinyabuzima ya mbere mu Rwanda no mu karere ko munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara yafunguwe mu Murenge wa Bwishyura mu Karere ka Karongi, mu Ntara y’Uburengerazuba mu Rwanda 

yafunguwe  yibandaga ku kumurika ibijyanye n’ingufu (Renewable and non renewable energy), urugendo rukorwa ngo zitange amashanyarazi n’ingaruka zigira ariko nyuma yaje kongerwamo ibijyanye n’inyamaswa n’amabuye y’agaciro byabaga i Kigali mu Ngoro y’Amateka kamere izwi nko kwa “Kandt”

Kuwa 7-10 Kanama 2019.<ref>http://mobile.igihe.com/ibidukikije/article/ibiteye-amatsiko-ku-ngoro-ndangamurage-y-ibidukikije-yihariye-muri-afurika</ref>.

== Intego z'ingoro ndangamurage y'ibidukikije ==
Hari zimwe mu ntego ingoro yashinzwe yiteze kugeraho ndetse zagiyihe ziyongera ari zo zikurikira :

* kumurika ibijyanye n’ingufu
* [[Dosiye:Ingoro.jpg|thumb|Ingoro ndangamurage y'ibidukikije yubatswe karongi ]]Kurengera ibidukikije 
* gusigasira bimwe mu bimera byagiye bicika bitakiboneka ahantu henshi .<ref>http://museum.gov.rw/index.php?id=5&L=1</ref>
* kurengera urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima harimo inyamaswa nk'inzoka ni ibindi <ref>http://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/144004</ref>


Umwihariko w'iyi ngoro niyo yambere y'ubatswe mu karere kibiyaga bigari ndetse na [[African Wildlife Foundation|africa]] muri rusange ishingiye kubidukikije no kubungabunga urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima n'ibimera .

